        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> We should probably not touch existing springboot-parent poms, as not sure who all using it.\n> \n> But wanted to have new springboot-parent (25) pom to have jdk11\n\nOk - I can do that - I'll just change springboot25 not to be generated from the template and change it directly.\n\nIn Jakarta, btw, my plan will be to change springboot2 to be the same as springboot25 and eventually get rid of 25 .. that 25 was just a stop gap since springboot 2.3 -> 2.5  was a breaking change due to some deprecated code being removed in 2.4",
